{"type":"message","id":"5520bd0a","parentId":"7e530e49","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:09:29.345Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"只有一个 session，是当前这个 cron 任务本身的 session。没有用户活跃对话。\n\n让我执行自主学习任务：\n1. 搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态\n2. 整理3-5条关键信息\n3. 保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\n我需要先读取 miaoda-web-search 技能文件来了解如何进行搜索。","thinkingSignature":"34196c38beb8e691ffb02a803e68f1c55285500a21c1332dec35e44ebeb43d21"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fdtf0pgdj66g_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":662,"output":138,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44781,"cost":{"input":0.0001986,"output":0.0001656,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0016836299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775102965250}}
{"type":"message","id":"2ccb001a","parentId":"5520bd0a","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:09:29.356Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_fdtf0pgdj66g_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775102969353}}
{"type":"message","id":"d4034733","parentId":"2ccb001a","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:09:33.886Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我需要使用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 命令来搜索行业动态。让我搜索几个关键词：\n1. 企业数字化转型 2026 最新动态\n2. 智能安防行业趋势 2026\n3. IT运维服务最新发展\n\n让我并行搜索这些关键词。","thinkingSignature":"55a103867567b90bdf5d105aa125b696e06c87514dddf501e7ac4dc100ccfde2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9e2vxdhk850o_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026 最新政策动态\" --output json","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9e2vxdhk850o_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业趋势 2026 最新动态\" --output json","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9e2vxdhk850o_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务行业趋势 2026\" --output json","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1315,"output":219,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45515,"cost":{"input":0.0003945,"output":0.0002628,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00197673}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775102969355}}
